{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You awaken as a Doll in a desolate, crumbling city with no memories. The path to the Royal Palace lies ahead, but hostile automatons and arcane golems stand in your way. To reach your destination, you must face three powerful foes, each guarding a crucial places of your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073480/extras/Book.gif?t=1734690103\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each encounter challenges you to make the most of your magic cards, artifacts, and skills. Choose your moves carefully, adapt to enemy patterns, and unleash powerful combos to overcome every foe. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073480/extras/Fight.gif?t=1734690103\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Before each run in Arcane Path, you\u2019ll choose one of 12  artifacts that shape your gameplay. Each artifact grants unique status effects, enhances starting cards with powerful bonuses, and adds thematic cards to your deck. Artifacts also influence battle rewards, ensuring key victories provide cards aligned with their theme, offering new strategies and playstyles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073480/extras/Artifacts.gif?t=1734690103\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong> 80+ unique cards with stunning hand-drawn illustrations.</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>3 large locations, each with its own distinct character and atmosphere. </strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>4 epic bosses, requiring unique strategies to defeat them. </strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong> 15+ enemy types, from standard automatons to mighty golems.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Two alternative endings.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dialogue system and interactive NPCs.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>13 story chapters with illustrations that immerse you in a captivating narrative.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Original soundtrack.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A blend of 2D and 3D hand-painted graphics, creating a stylish and vibrant visual experience. </strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073480/extras/Doll_Scream_long.png?t=1734690103\" /><u>Your fate may be crafted, but the final chapter is yours to write.</u></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073480/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734690103","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073480/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1734690103","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073480/dd8056c72f714d458821b1d844d42911777f85ff/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734690103","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073480/dd8056c72f714d458821b1d844d42911777f85ff/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1734690103","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You awaken as a Doll in a desolate, crumbling city with no memories. The path to the Royal Palace lies ahead, but hostile automatons and arcane golems stand in your way. To reach your destin